# Mobile App Family Rules

- Apply this rule when `projectFamily` is `mobile-app`.
- Read `docs/ai/project-bootstrap.md` and `docs/ai/stack-matrix.md` before changing mobile stack assumptions.
- Preserve platform config, signing, package naming, runtime env handling, and backend auth dependencies together.
- Treat `Flutter` as the default baseline and document exceptions when using React Native or native stacks.
- Keep device or simulator smoke validation in sync with deployment assumptions.
